<doc id="73385" wikidata="Q181234" url="?curid=73385" title="Castro Street">
<text>Castro Street may refer to:

* Castro Street in the Castro District, San Francisco, California
:* Castro Street Station, a Muni Metro underground station at the junction of Castro and Market streets in San Francisco
:* Castro Street Fair, a street fair in the Castro neighborhood
* Castro Street, the main street of Mountain View, Santa Clara County, California
* &quot;Castro Street&quot; (film), a 1966 short documentary film directed by Bruce Baillie and set in Richmond, California</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q956169" start="52" end="82" title="Castro District, San Francisco" label="Castro District, San Francisco"/>
<link wikidata="Q5050795" start="98" end="119" title="Castro Street Station" label="Castro Street Station"/>
